author: reinhard
msg: Set an entity resolver on the SAX parser that returns an empty input source. This prevents the SAX parser from accessing any URIs used in entities. That's definitely not the best solution because XMLCatalogs should be introduced but we have to find a solution that also works without Spring for C3 (in contrast to C2 where XML catalogs are configured via Spring mechanisms.).
